title: Head Case Designs Square Blue Classic Paisley Bandana Hybrid Case Compatible with Apple iPhone 7 Plus/iPhone 8 Plus
description: If you're looking for the case equivalent of a bullet-proof vest, this is it. Plastic backing means hardcore protection, whilst the form-fitting black rubber shell hugs your case close. Available in pretty much any design you can think of, this case is the perfect hybrid of fashion and function.
Our hybrid case is built tough so your device is protected from bumps and daily wear and tear, whilst adding a grip that won't slip.
With more than 8,000 original case designs to choose from, surround your device with a unique look that demands attention.
Durable multi-layer design combining a polycarbonate plastic back and high quality rubber body ensures your device stays safe from impact and external forces.
Knock knock, Who's there? Scratches. Scratches who? Exactly.
Simply slide your device into this flexible, form- fitting case that surrounds your device in all-over protection like a personal bodyguard! Your device will thank you for doing it such a huge favor.
Flexible, touch-sensitive gel shields volume and power buttons, whilst keeping ports and speakers fully accessible.
